<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="section-label">Questions</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Everything you <em>need to know.</em></h2>

    <div class="faq-list">

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What's actually in each Gummi gummy?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Each serving is 2 gummies. You get 3g of Creatine Monohydrate — the most clinically researched performance supplement in existence — plus Vitamin B6 to drive energy metabolism and support protein synthesis, and a precise Electrolyte blend to keep you hydrated and contracting at full capacity. That's the complete formula. No proprietary blends, no fillers, no stimulants.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Why a gummy instead of powder?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Creatine powder works — but most people don't take it consistently because mixing it is a hassle, the taste is gritty, and it's easy to skip. Gummi delivers your daily dose in a format you'll actually look forward to. No mixing, no measuring, no mess. You just chew two gummies and go. Consistency is what drives creatine's results, and consistency is what we're built around.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Will I retain water or feel bloated?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Some people notice mild water retention in the first week — this is creatine pulling water into your muscle cells, which is exactly what creates the fullness and strength you want. It's not the same as general bloating. At 3g per serving (below the high-loading doses that cause discomfort), most people experience very little, if any, initial water retention. Drink enough water daily and your body adapts quickly.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Do I need to do a loading phase?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">No. Loading phases (taking 20g/day for a week) were popularised to saturate muscles faster — but research shows that 3–5g daily reaches the same saturation level within 3–4 weeks with none of the digestive side effects that high loading doses cause. Gummi is designed for the consistent daily approach. Take two gummies every day and let the compound effect do its job.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          How long until I see results?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Most people notice improved strength, power output, and recovery within 2–4 weeks of consistent daily use. Creatine works by saturating your muscles over time — the longer you take it, the more pronounced the effect. Cognitive improvements (sharper focus, faster processing) often appear around the same window. Commit to at least 30 days and track your lifts — the numbers don't lie.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          How do I take them?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Two gummies per day — timing is flexible, but pre- or post-workout is ideal. What matters most is that you take them every single day, training day or not. Creatine builds up in your muscles over time, so skipping days slows down saturation. Do not exceed the recommended dose and keep out of reach of children.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Are they vegan, allergen-friendly, and safe?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes — Gummi is 100% vegan, gluten-free, and made with all-natural flavouring and colouring. No artificial preservatives, no nasties. Each batch is manufactured under strict quality controls. These statements have not been evaluated by SAHPRA and Gummi is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. If you are pregnant, nursing, on medication, or have a medical condition, consult your doctor before use.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What is your return policy?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">We stand behind Gummi with a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you use it consistently and don't notice a real difference in your performance within 30 days, contact us and we'll refund your full purchase — no return shipping required, no fine print. We offer this because we're confident it works, and we know that nothing builds trust like removing the risk entirely.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          How and when will my order arrive?
          <span class="faq-chevron">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="faq-answer-inner">Orders are processed within 24 hours and delivered across South Africa in 2–4 business days via The Courier Guy, PostNet, and Dawn Wing. Free delivery on orders over R500. You'll receive a tracking notification as soon as your order ships.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "FAQ" }]
}
{% endschema %}
